Here's an example code for swapping two elements in an array in JavaScript:

```javascript
function swap(arr, firstIndex, secondIndex) {
    let temp = arr[firstIndex];
    arr[firstIndex] = arr[secondIndex];
    arr[secondIndex] = temp;
}

// Example usage:
let array = [1, 2, 3, 4];
swap(array, 1, 2);  // after this, array is now [1, 3, 2, 4]
```
